Using Appimage
- download appimage from github

- make AppImage file executable
>> chmod +x FreeCAD_1.0.1-conda-Linux-x86_64-py311.AppImage

- extract AppImage
>> ./FreeCAD_1.0.1-conda-Linux-x86_64-py311.AppImage --appimage-extract

- rename extracted directory
>> mv squashfs-root freecad-1.0.1

- create launch script from freecad-launch.sh template

- create FreeCAD-1.0.1.desktop to run freecad-launch.sh
[Desktop Entry]
Name=FreeCAD-1.0.1
Exec=/media/david/MyDocs/freecad/appimage/freecad-launch.sh
Icon=/media/david/MyDocs/freecad/appimage/freecad-1.0.1/org.freecad.FreeCAD.svg
Type=Application
Terminal=false